    {
        "content": "<p>The mathlib style guide <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/contribute/style.html\">https://leanprover-community.github.io/contribute/style.html</a> has a section \"hypotheses left of colon\", which tells you to do exactly this.</p>",
